    "name": "Skillibeng",
    "profile": "Born on December 23, 1996, in St. Thomas, Jamaica.\r\nHe is a dancehall artist who began making music during his high school years. He initially worked at his father's business before focusing on music full-time after a serious car accident. His breakthrough came in 2019 with the single \"Brik Pan Brik.\" Since then, he has released numerous tracks and collaborated with both Jamaican and international artists. Skillibeng is known for his consistent output and for incorporating elements of rap and contemporary sounds into dancehall. He currently lives near Kingston to be closer to the music industry hub.",
